name: Peak Pharmaceuticals
short_description: Peak Pharmaceuticals, Inc. operates as a biopharmaceutical and nutraceutical company in the United States.
long_description: Peak Pharmaceuticals, Inc. operates as a biopharmaceutical and nutraceutical company in the United States. The company focuses to develop, manufacture, market, and sell medicinal products based on extracts from hemp. It is involved in the development of over-the-counter, THCfree, hemp based products for human market for the prevention and alleviation of symptoms associated with inflammatory and auto-immune diseases. The company was formerly known as Cannabis Therapy Corporation and changed its name to Peak Pharmaceuticals, Inc. in December 2014. Peak Pharmaceuticals, Inc. was incorporated in 2007 and is based in Scottsdale, Arizona.
